--- TESTCASE Verify Company ManagerId Is Null - 200 OK

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [200]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{CompaniesSection}}/{{CompanyId}}

--- TEST
await tp.Test("Company managerId should be null after manager was deleted.", async () =>
{
    dynamic body = await tp.Response.GetBodyAsExpandoAsync();
    Null(body.managerId);
});

--- END


